Subject: Stealth audit login error
Description:
We are not able to leverage windows login to authenticate to our stealth audit platform. We are prompted for username and password. anything entered is not accepted. 
we CAN log into the AIC but not the main audit web app.
Solution_Comment__c:
Issue:
Unable to login to the Enterprise Auditor reporting console at port 8082 with windows credentials.

Cause:
Credentials were stuck in a cache in the browser and not moving forward.

Resolution:
We removed the SSO through the browser in NEA and login was successful. You had mentioned that you preferred it to work this way so it was left as is.
